citation: Proclamation under the Tasmanian Health Service Act 2018 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Tasmanian Health Service Act 2018

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Tasmanian Health Service Act 2018 fix 1 July 2018 as the day on which the provisions of that Act commence.

18 June 2018

C. WARNER

Governor

By Her Excellency's Command,

Michael Darrel Joseph Ferguson

Minister for Health

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 27 June 2018
